From MOHIT K GOYAL Subject Re BusLogic questions Support for the BusLogic cards is not included with OS any Why not This is rather If you wish to install the beta from the CD ROM you will need to REM out the Adaptec device drivers as they have a nasty tendency to crash the BusLogic cards when OS attempts to use Thanks Adaptec That's cause the latest and presumably all future Adaptec drivers look for the string Adaptec or something to that effect in the cards